* {{enPR|mə-sī'ə}}, {{IPA|/məˈsaɪ.ə/}}, {{X-SAMPA|/m@"saI@/}}

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# {{context|Abrahamic tradition}} The one who is ordained by [[God]] to lead the people of [[Israel]], believed by Christians to be [[Jesus Christ]].
